{"serial": "13019", "department_serial": 14, "code": "FR2039", "class": "A", "name": {"en": "French Selected Readings II", "ch": "法文文選(二)"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "本課程僅提供法文系同學修課，作為華語文學分學程課程抵修，非法文系同學請勿修此門課。"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Hsu, Chi-Lin"], "ch": ["許綺玲"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "217"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": true, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "法國語文學系", "en": "Department of French"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 25, "remark": {"ch": "本課程僅提供法文系同學修課，作為華語文學分學程課程抵修，非法文系同學請勿修此門課。", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "在大一法文課程所奠定的基礎上，持續累積字彙，建立法文進階閱讀的基礎，進而培養文本的解析能力，使學生能夠在法文辭典的輔助下理解較為艱深的字句和文法，剖析文本的組織結構，解讀具備一定難度的文章和作品。", "en": "Aquerir la competence de comprehension de l’ecrit et une autonomie de l’etudiant face au foisonnement de textes en langue francaise."}, "outline": {"ch": "B組：延續大一法文文選課程，廣泛介紹各類型作品，上學期以青少年與兒童文學和童話故事為主，下學期以短篇小說為主。除艱難句意與文法結構的解析外，特別側重以下三個層面：文類特徵、修辭策略與敘述建構。A組：選文主要取自十九、二十世紀的法語文學文本。--上學期將選讀各類型文本，如抒情文、描寫文、敘事文、隨筆或雜感文、劇本，等名家作品選，以增進閱讀能力、充實詞彙、並經由文章多方接觸法國文化的各種面向。--下學期則以一個專題為中心，選不同作家的同主題文本，以進行主旨、書寫、觀點等各方面的文本分析和比較。", "en": "Travailler sur des textes litteraires de genres differents et de differents types ou autres pour que les etudiants en absorbent au fur et a mesure les structures, le lexique ou les modes d’expression.Chaque texte termine par un debat."}, "textbook": {"ch": "選文來源列舉：Charles Baudelaire, Pierre Loti, Henri Michaux, Guillaume Appolinaire, Louis Aragon, Raymond Queneau, Nathalie Sarraute, Jean-Paul Sartre, Roland Barthes, Marguerite Duras, Jean Tardieu, Georges Perec, Michel Tournier, Patrick Modiano, Le Clezio, Annie Ernaux, Brillat-SavarinVocabulaire 350 exercices, niveau superieur, Hachette", "en": "選文來源列舉：Charles Baudelaire, Pierre Loti, Henri Michaux, Guillaume Appolinaire, Louis Aragon, Raymond Queneau, Nathalie Sarraute, Jean-Paul Sartre, Roland Barthes, Marguerite Duras, Jean Tardieu, Georges Perec, Michel Tournier, Patrick Modiano, Le Clezio, Annie Ernaux, Brillat-SavarinVocabulaire 350 exercices, niveau superieur, Hachette"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "90", "en": "90"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1)評量採多元型式：包括隨堂問答、復習測驗、討論與回饋、心得交流、創意書寫等\n2)評量項目：字彙熟悉度與活用；正確的朗讀、斷句與發音；文章組織分析；內容思想方面的反思與回應；文辭風格的賞析等", "en": "1)Devoir sur la table, expose, test prealable, discussion, texte scriptible\n2)Vocabulaire, prononciation, articulaion, composition, analyse structurale et stylistique, comprehension thematique"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週二 8-10時 週三8-10時", "en": "mardi 8h-10h/ mercredi 8-10h"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "自主學習作業及評量", "en": "devoir  à la maison\névaluation"}, "domain": {"ch": "語言訓練 \n\n\n、\n\n\n文學\n\n\n、\n\n\n文化", "en": "語言訓練 \n\n\n、\n\n\n文學\n\n\n、\n\n\n文化"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "自學能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "多元文化觀", "rating": "(1)非常低", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "審美欣賞", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "創意思考", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯批判", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Competence in linguistic expression", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance", "Products/Creative Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Autodidactic ability", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", 